{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91faf642c2","title":"致贺龙、关向应电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"be8e740584","index":0,"year":1940,"month":4,"day":3,"articleId":"91faf642c2"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e84f82ab3e","name":"王震","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"00cef0a876","type":"paragraph","text":"致贺龙、关向应电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"91faf642c2"},{"id":"b9c8156676","type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年4月3日）李文九十军主要阴课是渡河袭取线德，威协延安，切断西北、华北交通。估计该军实行渡河时，高双成可能南下袭击绥德、米脂，日寇亦必乘虚攻击音西北。因此请考虑：（一）拒李防高抗日三方面如何布置兵力。（二）现有兵力总数是否足够应付严重局面（三）陈士梨支队如东调是否不感兵力不足。（四）王震旅无机动兵力如何解决。（五）王震河防部署及作战指挥统属你们负责。（六）为解决兵力不足是否有从路东调回若于部队之必要。请周详考虑电告。1","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"91faf642c2"}],"page":{"id":"3d61ca692f","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"91faf642c2","start":518,"end":518}}}},"__N_SSG":true}